{"about_the_game":"&quot;Blossom&quot; is an immersive case-solving game.<br><br>Early spring, 1999, Taoyuan Village.<br>In just several days, a series of drowning incidents occurred in the same quaint village. Then, on the night of the fifteenth day, numerous villagers witnessed a woman in red who bore an uncanny resemblance to a lady who had previously met an unjust demise...<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2579280/extras/\u8c1c\u6848_EN.jpg?t=1724038749\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>As a junior student at Qilin Normal University, you and your classmate, Wang Yishan, will venture to his hometown, Taoyuan Village, to work as volunteer teachers.<br></li><li>However, unbeknownst to you both, beneath the apparent tranquility, a storm that has been brewing for two decades is on the verge of erupting.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2579280/extras/\u9690\u60c5_EN.jpg?t=1724038749\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Each villager is guarding their secrets.<br></li><li>Pay close attention to their words and actions, delve deep into their pasts, and untangle their intricate web of deceit.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2579280/extras/\u7ebf\u7d22_EN.jpg?t=1724038749\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Every action has consequences, and every seemingly coincidental occurrence bears great significance.<br></li><li>Collect and analyze all the clues to uncover the truth beneath the surface.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2579280/extras/\u63a8\u51f6_EN.jpg?t=1724038749\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Relentlessly pursue the truth and eventually expose the true culprit. <br></li><li>However, you must also question whether the &quot;truth&quot; you uncover is indeed the whole